    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-16T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "5098a6e1e96ee0f318cc0f08b1bb19d5",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-16T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "Kerosene Lullaby wants a hushed first verse, almost spoken, before the band comes in.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-16T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "57f9e83f4443071f2340edeb933ab42c",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-16T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "5",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Kerosene Lullaby could pitch to the moody Americana lane — Keisha's harmony makes the chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-17T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b520511060dfae6bc8f0aa304c7fb1e0",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-17T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "6",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "Rio Nights got a full band demo at Copperline; Terrell's rough mix is in the Drive folder.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-17T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e7de2d97f24e6beb3fbf2ffcebd426f2",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-17T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "7",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Rio Nights should lean into a conjunto shuffle under the pre-chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-17T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c97459a3b608313160bed7f70880fb91",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-17T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "8",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Rio Nights is the up-tempo Tejano-country crossover — good pitch for a bilingual artist.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-18T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "2941a02627c0846a4b66a88311744d73",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-18T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "9",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "text": "Borderline Lonesome is demoed and honestly close; just need Terrell to tame the low end.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-18T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "53eff47f13a172311f4de10be4f7b1af",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-18T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "10",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "text": "On Borderline Lonesome, drop the drums out entirely for the last chorus and let the voice carry it.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-18T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a8a36850eceae15c836a7472b2dec256",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-18T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "11",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "text": "Borderline Lonesome pitches as a classic weeper — Vanessa wants to send it to the Silverbell list.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-19T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "97b15b45d65048abb9f25af0ed56a2c1",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-19T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "12",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "text": "Mockingbird Lane arrangement is locked; final vocal comp is with DT for approval.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-19T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "7bc4ee38a9ce7919fdd76ed6b4beda49",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-19T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "13",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "text": "Mockingbird Lane needs a bright Telecaster hook echoing the vocal melody in the intro.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-19T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "24053935c5ddbccbdcd88fc3f2e1aefb",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-19T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "14",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "text": "Mockingbird Lane is radio-leaning country — the hook lands fast, good for a lead single pitch.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-20T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "cc166ae748f40633422026ef530289e7",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "15",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "text": "Highway and the Kitchen Light is a rough draft; still humming the melody into voice memos.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-20T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e1324d03eb3657054afbc98b7efb592c",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "16",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "text": "Highway and the Kitchen Light could use a key change up a whole step for the final chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-20T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "3ed5c73884a35d487fe42c930ae1b0f9",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "17",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "text": "Highway and the Kitchen Light reads as a story-song — pitch it to an artist who tells stories.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-21T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "7cefe4c1e0ab2fa05c5907124debc15b",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-21T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "18",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "text": "Cafe de Olla Morning is demoed; the imagery came straight from Abuelita's kitchen in San Antonio.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-21T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "fba10f687b27e4eb876b2430f1f7dc05",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-21T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "19",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "text": "Cafe de Olla Morning wants a warm nylon-string guitar figure under the verses.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-21T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "32874485857ddf3518f47199a5678998",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-21T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "20",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "text": "Cafe de Olla Morning is a tender bilingual ballad — a nice change-of-pace pitch.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-22T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "cbac6fcac2e185de9ffa345f62bd27b6",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-22T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "21",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "text": "Saltillo Blue is drafted; the chorus melody is strong but the second verse is still rough.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-22T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c6424b9f34b60358810b0a3a82f9d21e",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-22T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "22",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Saltillo Blue should let the pedal steel bend into the title line every time.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-22T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c2449fd34c9e063fae9b5d0d002a2357",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-22T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "23",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "Saltillo Blue pitches as a lonesome highway cut — very traditional, very Texas.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-23T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "86111384e1c6318af604fea47ca074c2",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-23T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "24",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Conjunto Sunday lyrics are finished; ready to cut a scratch track with Keisha on harmony.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-23T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e009e15b3fde1f337945eb3844cdd83e",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-23T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "25",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Conjunto Sunday needs a real bajo sexto feel driving the two-beat.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-23T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "6b86216b4a0f7248c31ef33b514b2a3f",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-23T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "26",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "Conjunto Sunday is the most overtly Tejano thing I've got — pitch it where that's a feature.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-24T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "8b1ef394792da3b1b6a6efa61d77831e",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-24T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "27",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Boots by the Door got BGVs tracked; still deciding on the final key for the lead vocal.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-24T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "4a32d8a7791343fd4c3627ecb7affd2b",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-24T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "28",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "Boots by the Door wants a stomp-and-clap groove holding down the chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-24T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "26b230f33a7b8f329f2f0b15db432609",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-24T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "29",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Boots by the Door is an up-tempo kiss-off — fun pitch for a spitfire female vocalist.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-25T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "ec96b0fd5ccbdf263b82eb0e58f6611d",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-25T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "30",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Abuelita's Kitchen is demoed; wrote it thinking about Elena's Sunday pozole.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-25T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "32bccbf88566223a20cffef449301639",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-25T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "31",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "text": "Abuelita's Kitchen should open a cappella, just voice, before the accordion enters.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-25T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "20bbae5c0529c1af2bb4e43be5c72bb8",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-25T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "32",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "text": "Abuelita's Kitchen is a family memory song — pitch it as a deep album cut with heart.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-26T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "9f9b2667dab264e0b73e64793a3ae66e",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-26T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "33",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "text": "Mezcal Moon is mid-mix with Terrell; the groove finally feels right after the retracking.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-26T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "f29945b026386d537912f20212b66442",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-26T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "34",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "text": "Mezcal Moon needs a smoky trumpet line answering the hook, mariachi-style.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-26T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "33ff9ca002231834af126e72d54e1225",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-26T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "35",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "text": "Mezcal Moon pitches as a late-night border ballad — sultry and slow.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-27T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "01c1d155e90a21a315de610a9667f79a",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-27T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "36",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "text": "Pozole Sunday is through the mastering check; sounds warm on the car speakers.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-27T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "48b5e1ff29866b13c6695fa10991ff03",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-27T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "37",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "text": "Pozole Sunday wants a hand-percussion breakdown before the last verse.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-27T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "8469d6bdccdd0342eaad00d6389eec3d",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-27T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "38",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "text": "Pozole Sunday is a warm family-table song — good for a holiday or roots pitch.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-28T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "8aa604d3bd206072a0d1817e799a73ef",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-28T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "39",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "text": "Six Strings and a Prayer is in pitch prep; Vanessa flagged it as a Silverbell priority.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-28T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "2a8a386f1ea62453b7a26c2a5174c443",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-28T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "40",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "text": "Six Strings and a Prayer should build from solo guitar to a full gospel-tinged choir.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-28T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a34925b0a102211c133e0f9efb54b402",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-28T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "41",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "text": "Six Strings and a Prayer pitches as an inspirational country anthem — big, hopeful chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-29T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "485b40ef5ee6748f2f0383083f6482f8",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-29T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "42",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "text": "Tejano Twilight is demoed; the bounce is sitting in the shared Drive for notes.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-29T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "4174f030426b2973b126e7ce676dba4c",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-29T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "43",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "text": "Tejano Twilight wants an accordion and fiddle trading the instrumental turnaround.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-29T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "9cca69f8f7bb708d824ef1bb165721f4",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-29T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "44",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Tejano Twilight is the title-track energy — pure crossover, pitch it as a statement song.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-30T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c876aaf1792c2c70e973eaa0a7b9196a",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-30T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "45",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "San Antonio Sky needs a split sheet; Keisha co-wrote the bridge so we owe paperwork.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-30T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "f9de3af15b0ad0169b394dc90e1aee9c",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-30T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "46",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "San Antonio Sky should reach for a soaring falsetto on the final title line.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-06-30T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "5f4a0b9c04b57309b43a197e799c250e",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-06-30T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "47",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "San Antonio Sky is a hometown love letter — pitch it to a Texas-proud artist.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-01T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "db5db3a1aedbd0ceee5b37a3b5e338d3",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-01T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "48",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "The Silence He Left has finished lyrics; heavy one, wrote it about Dad.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-01T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "5c610177e8e179d6d48782c8ffb9d133",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-01T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "49",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "The Silence He Left wants long space between phrases — let the quiet do the work.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-01T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "9c5877c15ed3db635791401919c4d719",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-01T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "50",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "The Silence He Left pitches as a grief ballad — restrained, honest, no big production.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-02T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e4b8ed73436142a1fd359cc7bfecf0b1",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-02T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "51",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Cast Iron Heart got BGVs down; the chorus stacks are exactly what I heard in my head.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-02T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "7744259a42605107993f31417592a6b2",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-02T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "52",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Cast Iron Heart needs a gritty baritone guitar riff anchoring the verses.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-02T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "d7363ce75e492ffa432213956421fc3d",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-02T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "53",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fb",
    "text": "Cast Iron Heart is a tough, resilient anthem — pitch it as a defiant single.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-03T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "63ed18e733d88af0a9eca169a48059f2",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-03T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "54",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fc",
    "text": "Paloma in the Rain is through vocal comping; Keisha's harmony on the bridge is the moment.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-03T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b028cd2b7a7e9eea0651d8fc03eaaf0b",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-03T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "55",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fd",
    "text": "Paloma in the Rain should let a lone accordion cry over the intro.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-03T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "2941fc1a3ed0dc8f5c53d1ab79e8459b",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-03T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "56",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464fe",
    "text": "Paloma in the Rain pitches as a bilingual heartbreak ballad — delicate and cinematic.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-04T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "98c107be4c1ae8b0be0f1eb91afdc839",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-04T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "57",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18854464ff",
    "text": "Last Call Lullaby is mid-mix; trying to keep the barroom feel without it getting muddy.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-04T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "958812cc673cf06447bc1b1574a0fa65",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-04T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "58",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446500",
    "text": "Last Call Lullaby wants brushed drums and an upright bass walking under the verses.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-04T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "2abc2f6415dcbaac01c7d7bcb442ffc4",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-04T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "59",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446501",
    "text": "Last Call Lullaby pitches as a closing-time waltz — smoky, slow, three-quarter time.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-05T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "61d45c1fc45cbc441fd57fbfe4755ed8",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-05T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "60",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446502",
    "text": "Dust on the Fret is at the mastering check; last of the batch to get through.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-05T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "89a7b3e9caa63074c55bfccd133f47a7",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-05T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "61",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446503",
    "text": "Dust on the Fret should open on a single dry acoustic before the band swells in.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-05T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "3a8d69c8470984bd58eef95064512152",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-05T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "62",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446504",
    "text": "Dust on the Fret pitches as a road-worn troubadour song — pure and unhurried.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-06T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e7a742a76531d2582a35809bb20d67b8",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-06T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "63",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446505",
    "text": "Guadalupe Street is a fresh demo; named it after the walk to the West Side mercado.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-06T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "884d8ff3ced8eeb5ed4ff2d0a58a7aed",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-06T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "64",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446506",
    "text": "Guadalupe Street wants a marching snare and a horn stab on the chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-06T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "fc7d5303bf39892ce2cd3fcdf8685bc4",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-06T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "65",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1885446507",
    "text": "Guadalupe Street pitches as a proud barrio anthem — vivid, place-specific, alive.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-07T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e2b26f3be10d177c3aca5e1855425b51",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-07T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "66",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Ofrenda is demoed; wrote it around Día de Muertos for the ones we've lost.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-07T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "261b526aa91cef2b2bcd4559d8ad8c55",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-07T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "67",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "Ofrenda should build from a whisper to a full mariachi swell by the last chorus.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-07T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e3e9656dfcd9cb9e2473621efabe1843",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-07T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "68",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Ofrenda pitches as a reverent remembrance song — perfect for a fall or memorial release.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-07-08T15:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "538e41a08186d7fe5d0607179e13ed72",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-07-08T17:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "69",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Cumbia for the Broken is an early draft; the groove is undeniable, the lyric needs work.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  }
]
